<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="textpart" subtype="poem" n="III">
<l n="1"><milestone unit="para"/>Quamvis fluente dives auri gurgite  </l>
            <l n="2">non expleturas cogat avarus opes  </l>
            <l n="3">oneretque bacis colla rubri litoris  </l>
            <l n="4">ruraque centeno scindat opima <sic>bove</sic>,  </l>
             <l n="5">nec cura mordax deseret superstitem  </l>
            <l n="6">defunctumque <sic>leves</sic> non comitantur opes.  </l>



</div>